  <!-- ABOUT / TEXT BLOCKS -->
  <section id="about" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Concept Summary</h2>
        <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">___Humanity evolves from touch to clicks, from atoms to codes, transforming knowledge and identity. In that transmission phase, via design, C2W2 Runway tells a six-chapter story about our relationship with tech: how it first changes art, then devalues it through mass production, and finally forces a search for new meaning and identity. The click is the new biology.</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">___C2W2 is a 30-minute browser-based runway. No downloads, no logins. Out of seventy-five, selected forty-eight avatars appear in a six-chapter sequence, with hyper-real textile simulations and a clear narrative spine.
___The work merges digital fashion, architecture, and performance into one continuous environment. Each chapter marks a step in the evolution of identity, material, and medium in virtual culture.</pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 mt-8">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">World Insights</h2>
        <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">___The metaverse space is a minimalist, dark environment with dramatic circular lighting, evoking a digital void where avatars evolve. Avatars rotate 360 degrees and walk in 15 meter radius loops during 30 seconds each, and each has a central object related to the design. Each chapter builds on the last: starting with AI-reimagined art classics, shifting to experimental digital fashion, blending NFTs and figures, resetting with pure AI generation, ascending minimally, and rebirth through transformed echoes.</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Runway Parts</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-2 text-white/80 text-sm">
          <li>Evolution Of Medium Of Traditional Art</li>
          <li>Virtual Fashion</li>
          <li>Evolution Of Medium Of Art As Nft</li>
          <li>AI Powered Design</li>
          <li>Transhumanism</li>
          <li>Evolution Of Art As Mutant Meaning</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

