          <li>Runs fully in a web browser on-chain</li>
          <li>Single link includes all modes</li>
          <li>48 GLB / VRM garments</li>
          <li>Originally built on Hyperfy v1 → rebuilt with Three.js</li>
          <li>Mintable as an HTML-based NFT</li>
        </ul>
