        <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Files stored permanently on Arweave (PFADI), minted on Ethereum</li>
          <li>First metaverse experience minted & viewable directly in marketplace windows</li>
          <li>First use of dynamic Clo3D textiles in a standard browser environment</li>
          <li>C2W2 = Click-to-Wear Season 2</li>
        </ul>
